      <scopecontent id="aspace_4712a7b622136c642df65fe815a0051b">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The materials consist photographs and pictures of Street Hall at Yale (formerly known as the Art Building). Included are views of construction, studios, galleries, and classrooms.</p>  
